Package org.apache.maven.shared.dependency.tree

Interface Summary
DependencyTreeBuilder Builds a tree of dependencies for a given Maven project.
 

Class Summary
DefaultDependencyTreeBuilder Default implementation of DependencyTreeBuilder.
DependencyNode Represents an artifact node within a Maven project's dependency tree.
DependencyTree Deprecated. As of 1.1, replaced by the dependency tree root DependencyNode
DependencyTreeInverseIterator Iterator for DependencyNode implementing a traversal from leaves to root.
DependencyTreePreorderIterator Iterator for DependencyNode implementing a preoder traversal.
DependencyTreeResolutionListener An artifact resolution listener that constructs a dependency tree.
 

Exception Summary
DependencyTreeBuilderException Indicates that a Maven project's dependency tree cannot be resolved.
